Ukraine regional geometry bundled for EVA Assistant

File:
- ukraine_alert_regions.geojson

Source:
- geoBoundariesSimplified.geojson from https://github.com/sergeiown/Map_with_Marker_Clusters
- Original geodata attribution in that project points to https://www.geoboundaries.org

